NOBODY helped so i worked it out myself ..After un packing with winrar -you will get the cue file which doesnt work for me! and the bin file ..Mount the CUE file (image) from disk 1 with Daemon tools then from the folder produced ,drag the "AVSEQ01.dat" file (which is the film in ".avi") to your desktop (copying will take 3 minutes or so ) Then rename it to disk 1 .Then repeat process for disk 2 .Then open up nero vision express and burn to dvd as usual !   Next time please could "noodles "make a cue file what actually works to save all this bother  ..but apart from that a good release thanks.Maxi
